Project Title: The LaunchPad
What does it do?
It plays a part of a song when a key is pressed on the grid so that the entire song can be played. It
has a button that allows the user to change the “page” its on so that many different songs can be
saved onto the launchpad or if there are not enough keys on the grid for the song.
What are it's features?
A button that allows the user to change “pages”
A grid with many keys that plays a part of a song through a speaker when pressed
Song can be saved on it and stays even after it has been powered off
What will you make?
CAD Design, Graphics
Casing design, grid design, housing, casing,
Laser cutting
Casing for the launchpad
3D Printing
Keys for the launchpad,
Micro-controller
Push-button presses, readings, play speaker,
Input devices
Push-button switches
Output devices
8-ohm speaker
